{
  "title":"Temperature",
  "date":"2005-03-04 CST",
  "origin":"Funny Logic",
  "url":"text-temperature",
  "author":"Ryan X. Charles"
}



			
				<p>Whilst at school, a classmate said the following:</p>

	<p>&#8220;When it&#8217;s Cold outside, does Hot get jealous?&#8221;</p>

	<p>&#8220;Obviously,&#8221; said his alter-ego. &#8220;Summer is when Hot gets his revenge.&#8221;</p>

	<p>Both of them were me, of course.</p>

		
		

